=== IR Program ===

Function: somme
Parameters: a, b
function somme:
    param a
    param b
    t0 = a + b
    return t0
end function

Function: double
Parameters: x
function double:
    param x
    t1 = 2
    t2 = x * t1
    return t2
end function

